<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90272745-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799a"><num value="2799a">§ 2799a.</num><heading> CFE Treaty obligations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The authorities provided in this subchapter shall be exercised consistent with the obligations incurred by the United States in connection with the CFE Treaty.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90272746-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/629">Pub. L. 90–629</ref>, ch. 9, § 92, as added <ref href="/us/pl/102/228/s2">Pub. L. 102–228, § 2</ref>, <date date="1991-12-12">Dec. 12, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/1691">105 Stat. 1691</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
